<!-- ADACEnumeratedTypes_Generic.xsd - contains all SimpleDataTypes for the Relaxed Implementation of ADAC 5.0.1
using only the basic data types for each constrained property. 
Replacing references to ADACEnumeratedTypes.xsd with this module ADACEnumeratedTypes_Generic.xsd will result 
in a relaxed validation without enumerations enforced.  This may be useful when dealing with legacy data that 
does not conform to current constraints.
Jurisdictions with State implemntation needs must edit and maintain these types according to need in ADACEnumeratedTypes.xsd
No SimpleType may be added, removed or renamed as such action will invalidate the ADAC structure
No SimpleType may have its base datatype changed as such action will invalidate the ADAC structure
IPWEAQ and the ADAC Strategic Reference Group must approve all regional implementation changes.   -->
